rry Lefebvre, Dao Nguyen, and James Hardcastle provided valuable collaboration throughout the process. A formal consultation process was held with sustainable tourism stakeholders.", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "e4f51a69-749c-4664-b07a-3c2e085b85b5": {"__data__": {"id_": "e4f51a69-749c-4664-b07a-3c2e085b85b5", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/resources/grey-literature/one-health-principles-sustainable-tourism-protected-and-conserved-areas", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "One Health principles for sustainable tourism in protected and conserved areas", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/resources/grey-literature/one-health-principles-sustainable-tourism-protected-and-conserved-areas", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "6afc1971d136c10b265c2d924c5389c3ccbf0d18685e6e0d45e8df36ed79b042"}, "2": {"node_id": "b81547f8-1770-4472-af8b-79ad5cb3a6f3", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/resources/grey-literature/one-health-principles-sustainable-tourism-protected-and-conserved-areas", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "e38433a21984f30dfede4cc3bed5c28d47d1993941164a044afce437cbab8a10"}}, "hash": "8f89d7e2126eee9e3741be5eb5ad3546203ec162c03491c18b066022b72b5178", "text": "A formal consultation process was held with sustainable tourism stakeholders. The following experts are thanked for their val